# ROSE Playbook Design System (2026)

Modern, professional SaaS aesthetic with layered depth and restraint.

## Design Principles
1. **Restraint** - Brand colors accent, don't dominate
2. **Layered Depth** - Soft backgrounds with elevated white cards
3. **Consistency** - Same spacing, shadows, radii everywhere
4. **Stability** - Fixed modal sizes, no layout shifts

---

## Color System

### Philosophy
Use brand colors (Oxford Blue, Gold) **sparingly** on soft backgrounds. They should POP, not overwhelm.

### Brand Colors
| Color | Hex | CSS Variable | Usage |
|-------|-----|--------------|-------|
| Oxford Blue | `#14213D` | `text-oxford-blue` | Headings, primary buttons, important text |
| Gold | `#FEC872` | `text-gold` | Accents, highlights, CTAs, hover states |
| Gold Light | `#FFE0A3` | `bg-gold-300` | Soft backgrounds, badges |

### Background Layers
| Color | Hex | CSS Class | Usage |
|-------|-----|-----------|-------|
| Page Background | `#F8F7F5` | `bg-background` | Main page background |
| Surface | `#FFFFFF` | `bg-card` | Cards, modals, elevated elements |
| Surface Muted | `#F3F2F0` | `bg-surface-muted` | Sidebar, secondary areas |

### Text Colors
| Color | Hex | CSS Class | Usage |
|-------|-----|-----------|-------|
| Foreground | `#14213D` | `text-foreground` | Primary text |
| Muted | `#6B7280` | `text-muted-foreground` | Secondary text, descriptions |

