## Component Patterns

### Cards (Shadcn `Card`)

**Variants:**
| Variant | Usage |
|---------|-------|
| `default` | Standard elevated card |
| `elevated` | More prominent shadow |
| `outline` | Bordered, no shadow |
| `ghost` | Minimal, for empty states |
| `accent` | Gold top border accent |

```jsx
// Standard card
<Card className="h-full">

// Accent card (for playbook/process items)
<Card variant="accent" className="hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">

// Empty state
<Card variant="ghost" className="bg-muted/30">
```

### Modals (Shadcn `Dialog`)

**Fixed Sizes - NEVER Resize:**
| Size | Width | Use Case |
|------|-------|----------|
| `sm` | 400px | Confirmations, simple forms |
| `md` | 560px | Standard forms, settings |
| `lg` | 720px | Complex content, collaborators |

```jsx
<Dialog open={open} onOpenChange={setOpen}>
  <DialogContent size="md">
    <DialogHeader>
      <DialogTitle>Title</DialogTitle>
    </DialogHeader>
    <DialogBody> {/* Scrollable content area */}
      {/* Content here */}
    </DialogBody>
    <DialogFooter>
      <Button>Action</Button>
    </DialogFooter>
  </DialogContent>
</Dialog>
```

### Buttons

```jsx
// Primary (Oxford Blue)
<Button className="bg-oxford-blue hover:bg-oxford-blue/90">

// Accent (Gold)  
<Button className="bg-gold text-oxford-blue hover:bg-gold/90">

// Outline
<Button variant="outline" className="border-oxford-blue text-oxford-blue">

// Destructive
<Button variant="outline" className="text-destructive border-destructive">
```

